      • reset

        public void reset(java.lang.String sequenceName)
           throws ApplicationException
        从接口复制的说明: UUIDService
        Clear the cached sequence. After reset(), both requests to UUIDService.getTicketSerialNo(int) , UUIDService.getGeneralID() and UUIDService.getReferenceNo(int) will query new sequence range from underlying database.
        指定者:
        reset 在接口中 UUIDService
        参数:
        sequenceName - Reset the sequence with given name( Sequence.NAME_TICKETSERIALNO, Sequence.NAME_GENERAL). If sequenceName is null, then this operation will reset all sequences.
        抛出:
        ApplicationException
